<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('../partials/app_head') %>
</head>
<body class="app-shell min-h-screen text-cocoa">
    <div class="relative flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center overflow-hidden px-6 py-10">
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
            <div class="absolute -left-20 top-0 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-emerald-100/60 blur-3xl"></div>
            <div class="absolute right-0 top-1/4 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-amber-100/50 blur-3xl"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/3 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-lime-100/40 blur-3xl"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative w-full max-w-2xl">
            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[32px] border border-stone-200/80 bg-white/90 shadow-2xl shadow-stone-200/50 backdrop-blur">
                <div class="border-b border-stone-100 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-50 via-white to-amber-50 px-6 py-6 sm:px-8 sm:py-7">
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-amber-200 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-amber-700 shadow-sm">
                        Error Page
                    </div>

                    <h1 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-stone-900 sm:text-4xl">
                        404 - Page Not Found
                    </h1>

                    <p class="mt-3 max-w-xl text-sm leading-7 text-stone-600 sm:text-base">
                        Halaman yang kamu cari tidak ditemukan, mungkin link-nya salah, halaman sudah dipindah, atau route-nya belum tersedia.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="px-6 py-8 sm:px-8 sm:py-8">
                    <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
                        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-stone-200 bg-stone-50 p-4">
                            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-stone-500">Status</p>
                            <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-stone-900">404</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-stone-200 bg-stone-50 p-4">
                            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-stone-500">Condition</p>
                            <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-stone-900">Not Found</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-stone-200 bg-stone-50 p-4">
                            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-stone-500">Suggestion</p>
                            <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-stone-900">Go Back</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
                        <a
                            href="/dashboard"
                            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-stone-900 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-stone-300/40 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-emerald-700"
                        >
                            Go to Dashboard
                        </a>

                        <a
                            href="javascript:history.back()"
                            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-stone-300"
                        >
                            Go Back
                        </a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-8 rounded-3xl border border-stone-200 bg-stone-50 p-4">
                        <p class="text-sm leading-7 text-stone-600">
                            Coba cek kembali URL yang kamu buka, atau lanjutkan dari dashboard untuk kembali ke halaman yang tersedia.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>